From humble beginnings as a Nintendo add-on to the most dominant gaming console of all time, this is our look back at the entire history of the Sony PlayStation. Between the incredible domination of the PlayStation 1 and PlayStation 2 through the rocky times of the PlayStation 3 and PS Vita and finally onto the resurrection of the PlayStation brand with the PS4 settle in for one of our biggest videos ever.
